                <span class="problems-badge">NORTH YORK-SPECIFIC ISSUES</span>
                <h2>What Are the Top 5 Appliance Problems in North York?</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Serving 672,000 residents across Willowdale, Don Mills, Sheppard, York Mills, Bayview Village, Thornhill, Bathurst Manor, and Flemingdon Park. Expert solutions for North York's unique challenges.</p>
